== Kickback

Applies when: +
@ hearts agreed, or
@ minor agreed and 4m not a jump
 
=== Diamonds and Hearts

If we have agreed diamonds and are at 3D, then: +
@ 4D is not a jump, so not minorwood +
@ 4H is a jump so it is kickback

If we have agree diamonds and are above 3D, then 4H is kickback
#provided that hearts were not bid on the first round#.

Otherwise, 4H is an offer-to-play and 4S is kickback unless spades
were also bid on the first round.

[TIP]
====
4H is needed as an offer-to-play when a 3H bid is unavailable and
hearts were bid on the first round.
====

****
.Need discussion

If hearts and spades were both bid on the first round, then we need to
choose our agreement from: +

@ no KC ask +
@ always 4H +
@ least in-focus major via special rules
****

