=== Exclusion

Applies when:

@ direct triple-jump response to 1M opening
@ suit agreed, then jump +
@ a non-jump following
>> a control-bid by partner
>> suit agreement at 4-level

Responses:  0, 1, 2-, 2+, 3-, 3+

