|===

&DEPO example&

If trump = {S} and interference = 5{H} then +
@ Dble = 0, 2{OrLess}, or 4 (even)
@ Pass = 1 or 3 (odd)
@ 5{S} = 2 with trump Q

Following Pass (odd) it is still possible to ask for the trump Q with
double.

